    \** ------------- **\

    {L5}     === (n,n̩)    * m       * n(j,J)     * ŋ
    {_L5_}   === CIRTH_12 * CIRTH_6 * CIRTH_17   * CIRTH_22
    {L5}     --> {_L5_}

    \** ------------- **\

    {L6}       === w
    {_L6_}     === CIRTH_44
    {L6}       --> {_L6_}

    {L6_NASAL}   === nw
    \if "english_nw == ENGLISH_NW_TREAT_NORMALLY"
